## Implementation Guide

### Adding PMax Negative Keywords

1. Navigate to PMax campaign
2. Go to "Asset groups" tab
3. Click on asset group name
4. Scroll to "Negative keywords" (may need to expand "Show more settings")
5. Click "+ Add negative keywords"
6. Paste list of terms (one per line)
7. Select match type (Exact recommended for cannibalization issues)
8. Click "Save"

**Note**: PMax negatives are asset group-level, not campaign-level.

